Global Alpha Antitrypsin Deficiency Treatment Market Insights
Alpha Antitrypsin Deficiency Treatment Market size was valued at USD 1.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.7 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 8.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Alpha Antitrypsin Deficiency Treatment Market Overview
The global Alpha Antitrypsin Deficiency Treatment Market was valued at approximately USD 1.2 billion in 2024 and is projected to reach USD 2.3 billion by 2032, growing at a CAGR of 8.5% during the forecast period. This market growth is driven by the increasing awareness of Alpha Antitrypsin Deficiency (AATD), advancements in therapeutic options, and the rising global incidence of chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD) linked to the condition. The introduction of novel biologic therapies and improved diagnostic tools is also significantly boosting market expansion.

